metadata.name: Hazy Reflections #1/10
metadata.description:
‘Hazy Reflections’ was inspired by a seemingly endless relationship with late nights and heavy mornings. The intention was to capture the flashpoint between empowerment and fragility, whilst leaving room for interpretation of the subjects exact circumstances. 

This piece is the first artwork from Tabu’s inaugural NFT series, ‘I Am Me’, which explores female independence, sexuality and empowerment.
